      <textAnnotation id="sid-597B3AD0-7C66-4219-80EF-7D086DF9F3AE" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Check Supply and check allocation both are happening in the same call  in BY</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-232701A8-7F00-4C49-9EDA-1D4E594544F4" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP 
S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EDD313B9-CEF4-498D-996F-ECA2CB2C20C2" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP 
S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F9D2ECED-B70D-4F40-AD0E-A7B6DC07CC9A" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-56FCDE19-966F-466F-BF25-D96DE33DD1BA" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>
1. SO1 CDD = CMAD + TPT
2. SO1 CMAD received from BYOP in batch processes this SO1 CMAD could be dampened. 
3. SO1 Realtime ATP are not subject to dampening rules. 


</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9CDA570A-2C2E-4FE1-9151-E86826108759" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP 
S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C5CF545E-C030-4BEF-935D-80844D1691F7" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>All Products expect VMI KE and invoice only item categories will go to BYOP for Supply and Allocation</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2EB696B0-25CF-4BC8-9B82-517529539D82" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>BY relevance check more related to Master data
 </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-BF0F3C1B-F8E8-4A7C-B5EE-FD82EBC1EFE9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If connection error between BYOP and S4, then user will get an error message in ATP screen, error will be logged in report</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-439A030A-FFFF-4A7A-9691-FC704FB67311" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP 
S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9E94297B-5956-407B-876A-0964BA7E952D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1) From Change order - (assumptions) 
if there was a previous it commit will remain 
2) From Create order - no sales order generated</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6E3F6371-4BA5-44DB-9701-E98F405EFAEF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1) From Change order - (assumptions) if there was a previous it commit will remain 
2) From Create order - no sales order generated</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-79523B0B-1EC7-4943-A560-D2E6A7CD031D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.If Product Sub is agreed with customer and if original MMID is not available then BYOP will look to fulfill SOLI with alternate MMID, which will be updated in the SOLI if the user accepts results.
 2. Original SOLI MMID can be found in Material entered field in Sales A Tab of that SOLI 
3.If user has applied and saved Fixed Material, Fixed Plant and DNI flag to SOLI in real time, then in either real time or batch ATP, BYOP will adhere to these settings when determine CMAD.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9DD44BB1-972F-49D6-B843-C83674352ED5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This step only applies to real time ATP</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-877C00DF-5F50-497F-9673-FC4DCB6543FB" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP 
S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EAAF02CF-5744-4361-95A9-695DBBC11A9C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/04b83b1aa5da43179b6ed26475955f26</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Blue Yonder
 SPM</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-65410961-1074-4FBB-92AF-FBD21E0433A6" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7547F01B-43AC-45B5-8BCA-3AED47AAC798" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Logistics wrapper program will apply for 2DN model</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-49807D9D-3B96-4B12-90E8-CA4DFE9677A9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SO2 process also applies</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-1805393A-2917-4338-9620-536DB77B395C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SO2 could be created up to 13 days prior to SO1 CMAD</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E087A287-C774-4CF1-A18F-53DC4C3874A5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>. If user saves results and CDD has changed, an acknowledgement will be sent.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3DF0425C-81A0-4D23-AECB-15DB70B2494A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this activity can be done manually or automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3D04FFF8-60B5-4A4A-89F5-E12B5C814F88" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this activity can be done manually or automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-998252D2-58B1-43DA-A7E0-71A496E733D1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this activity can be done manually or automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9229B504-7ACC-4750-ADF3-BA6C97BA8F5B" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/04b83b1aa5da43179b6ed26475955f26</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="right" bottom="false" left="true" ref="text_name" right="false" top="false" valign="middle" x="-7.0" y="29.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Blue 
Yonder 
SPM</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4D225FD0-0B3A-45A9-8199-75EE0EA66F89" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/04b83b1aa5da43179b6ed26475955f26</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="right" bottom="false" left="true" ref="text_name" right="false" top="false" valign="middle" x="-7.0" y="29.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Blue 
Yonder 
SPM</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E86E0408-F57D-4FBB-AACF-86AED368D92F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Supply Allocation Report is reviewed based on customer segmentation/ prioritization logic</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-725E3AD6-9FB5-4631-8A28-C4D5CE9068C2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This step occurs only if product is place "on" allocation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E6881734-E35A-47B5-8027-0499D58CB58B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>There will be a manual escalation process (outside of nightly reprocessing) where a CBA can raise only critical orders (not everything) Scope of escalaltion file: Customer orders confirmed &amp; unconfirmed within the promise horizon Products on and off allocation Requires stronger justification than CMAD &gt;RMAD Excludes RTF and supply escalations (AR - Supply health escalations process TBD )</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-916643F6-F632-456A-AD95-D8C2ECDAE4FE" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Planners will be proactively reviewing Orders without CMAD / RDD vs CDD /Allocation and demand</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-68b7da64-c663-41d2-bdc5-baca191f2774" id="sid-CAFC35B9-3635-4281-9FD2-4C34ED0F2C0C">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
   </process>
